Package com.facebook.buck.features.project.intellij

Class IjProjectSourcePathResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.sourcepath.resolver.impl.AbstractSourcePathResolver
      • com.facebook.buck.features.project.intellij.IjProjectSourcePathResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SourcePathResolver
    public class IjProjectSourcePathResolver
extends AbstractSourcePathResolver
    A SourcePathResolver implementation that uses only information found in the target graph when converting a BuildTargetSourcePath to an outputPath. This allows the IjProject code to rely only on the TargetGraph when constructing a project.
